[I] A Javascript binding for GNOME

[T] Gjs is a Javascript binding for GNOME. It's mainly based on Spidermonkey
[T] javascript engine and the GObject introspection framework.

[U] https://wiki.gnome.org/JavaScript

[A] The GNOME Project
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool extra/desktop/gnome

[L] GPL
[V] 1.89.1
[P] X -----5---9 151.799

[CV-URL] https://download.gnome.org/sources/gjs/cache.json
[D] 6b7d3154f7555b2b0cdbc3135d6c43d5c4a1cf5f0ca1a214df669649 gjs-1.89.1.tar.xz https://download.gnome.org/sources/gjs/1.89/

. $base/package/*/*/gnome-conf.in
jsver=$(pkgprefix ver mozjs)
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -DXP_UNIX=1
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -I$root/$(pkgprefix includedir mozjs)/mozjs-${jsver%%.*}/js
